message.content:
1. Seventy older women participated in the investigation.
2. The women were randomly assigned to one of three groups.
3. One group was given whey protein before resistance training (RT) and a placebo after RT (WP-PLA).
4. The WP-PLA group consisted of 24 women.
5. Another group was given a placebo before RT and whey protein after RT (PLA-WP).
6. The PLA-WP group consisted of 23 women.
7. The third group was given a placebo before and after RT (PLA-PLA).
8. The PLA-PLA group also consisted of 23 women.

messages.content:
Statement: Seventy older women participated in this investigation and were randomly assigned to one of three groups: whey protein pre-RT and placebo post-RT (WP-PLA, n = 24), placebo pre-RT and whey protein post-RT (PLA-WP, n = 23), and placebo pre- and post-RT (PLA-PLA, n = 23).
